APIs
NCBI provides several public APIs that allow programmatic access to many
databases and tools.
Entrez Programming Utilities (E-utilities)
The E-utilities are the public API to the NCBI Entrez system and allow access to all Entrez databases
including PubMed, PMC, Gene, Nuccore and Protein. The E-utilities are a suite of eight server-side
programs that accept a fixed URL syntax for search, link and retrieval operations. A companion package
named Entrez Direct consists of several executables that allow the E-utilities to be called directly from
a UNIX command line.
